overview: Them dirty Trailer Trash Boys are up to it again. This time it's a no-nonsense buffet of Bareback Buttfuckers starring some of the nastiest boys from the trailer park. Tattooed hunks Ryan Sebastian, Isaac X, Buck Richards, and Andrew Delta join the smoother young dudes Alfonso Osnaya, Grant Ducati, Jonah Wheeler, Colton Blue, and Greg Riley. This is gonna be ffffuuuunnnn.
title: Bareback Buttfuckers
